name: Reflection (Golden)
description:
I am sitting in a cafe and I am surrounded by tens, hundreds, thousands of people.
But none of them notice my presence.
Everyone is busy with their own problems.
And only when someone accidentally touches my hand, I instantly respond, and like in slow motion I see a person who has just touched me.
It was as if I was in zero gravity and it made me slightly swayed.
In the reflection that I saw at that moment, I did not even understand what had happened.
Just something flashed like a mirage...
